title: Countdown - December 1989 (gnv64)
description: Countdown - December 1989 English | PDF | 54 pages | 9.3 mb scanned to PDF by me. This is an old Australian music magazine that I have had with me. Just scanned it recently. Will be of inerest to people who fancy music of the 80's. Like most standard music magazines, it contains news 7 reviews of the bands & music of that current era. Remember that it was the era of cassettes & LPs. CDs were a new thing then! You will find bands like Roxette, the Beatmasters, Kylie, Bros, etc. There is also a COUNTDOWN POP-POLL for 1989. Happenong TV series, movies & videos are also reviewed in addition to albums, While scanning, I have skipped the irrelevant ads.
